casebody.data:
Interstate Brands Corporation, Appellant, v. D.L. Peterson Trust Company et al., Appellees.

[Cite as Interstate Brands Corp. v. D.L. Peterson Trust Co. (1989), 43 Ohio St. 3d 174.]

(No. 88-1305 Submitted April 4 , 1989 Decided June 14, 1989.) Crahbe, Brown, Jones, Potts & Schmidt, Gilbert J. Gradisar and John C. Albert, for appellant. Wiles, Doucher, Van Burén & Boyle Co., L.P.A., Thomas E. Boyle and Kevin R. Bush, for appellees.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on authority of Cincinnati Bell Tel. Co. v. Straley (1988), 40 Ohio St. 3d 372, 533 N.E. 2d 764.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Douglas, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Holmes and Wright, JJ., dissent.
